data.description: Beautiful Brick Ranch with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. This home sits privately on 2.21 acres of land with a 2 car attached garage as well as a 3 car detached garage! The sunken living room and the remodeled kitchen feature an open floor plan and fantastic living space. The master suite has a remodeled bathroom with large tile walk-in shower. On the exterior there is a covered front porch and a brand new back patio. Roof was replaced in 2022.
